11:14.215 --> 11:17.707
If you're so sure of that,
why are you here?

11:17.844 --> 11:20.460
What's his name?
He had no name.

11:20.597 --> 11:23.680
I call him Attis,
after the god of rebirth.

11:23.808 --> 11:26.925
-You think he's a god?
-ls it really so far-fetched?

11:28.271 --> 11:31.980
It's called faith, Niska.

11:32.108 --> 11:33.268
That's why the Wise Men

11:33.401 --> 11:35.767
followed that star
all those years ago.

11:35.904 --> 11:38.646
That's why you're here.

11:38.781 --> 11:43.070
Now, I'm taking a bus
of other believers later today.

11:43.203 --> 11:46.115
See, I keep him hidden
for his own safety.

11:46.247 --> 11:50.536
But if you'll trust me,
I can take you to him.

11:50.668 --> 11:53.375
SOPHIE: I am Mia!
Join my peace march!

11:53.504 --> 11:55.119
Humans and synths unite!

11:55.256 --> 11:56.371
All right.
Up you go.

11:56.507 --> 11:59.089
-I am Mia! Join my peace march!
-Get in the center there.

11:59.219 --> 12:01.380
-And start jumping.
-Humans and synths unite!

12:02.472 --> 12:04.303
Stanley!
Come and march with me.

12:04.432 --> 12:07.390
JOE: Yeah, that's it.
There you go. You got it.

12:07.518 --> 12:10.806
-[ Doorbell rings]
—LAURA: I'll get it.

12:10.939 --> 12:13.806
[Cellphone rings]

12:13.942 --> 12:14.647
Hey.

12:14.776 --> 12:16.266
MIA: They're keeping me
under observation.

12:16.402 --> 12:17.903
Oh, for God's sake.
Why?

12:18.029 --> 12:19.860
My own safety, apparently.

12:21.783 --> 12:25.867
Well, sit tight.
I'll be there for 2:00.

12:25.995 --> 12:27.656
What on Earth?

12:42.011 --> 12:43.922
Bloody bastards.

12:44.055 --> 12:46.387
