-[ Bones cracking ]

13:02.448 --> 13:03.699
Go inside, please, Laura.

13:03.825 --> 13:04.985
Stanley!

13:05.576 --> 13:08.283
[Men grunting]

13:08.413 --> 13:09.528
[Choking]

13:09.664 --> 13:11.529
[ Metal creaks, gate closes ]

13:16.838 --> 13:19.170
Go inside, please, Laura.

13:28.558 --> 13:30.014
[Line ringing]

13:33.396 --> 13:34.602
[Grunting]

13:34.731 --> 13:36.687
OPERATOR: 999 --
what's your emergency?

13:36.816 --> 13:39.523
[Gagging]

13:47.076 --> 13:48.452
[Gasps]

13:54.709 --> 13:56.495
[ Door closes ]

13:59.380 --> 14:02.042
There is no longer
anything to fear, Laura.

14:02.175 --> 14:03.915
The situation
has been dealt with.

14:05.386 --> 14:06.546
How did that happen?

14:09.891 --> 14:13.634
How did what happen, Laura?

14:13.770 --> 14:14.976
You were angry.

14:15.104 --> 14:17.356
I am not programmed
to experience anger.

14:17.482 --> 14:19.268
What you witnessed
was passive resistance.

14:19.400 --> 14:21.391
That wasn't passive.

14:21.527 --> 14:25.395
That wasn't resistance.

14:25.531 --> 14:26.737
I am not programmed to --

14:26.866 --> 14:29.528
Sit down, Stanley, please.

14:41.130 --> 14:44.167
Will that be all, Laura?

14:45.635 --> 14:46.670
No.

15:11.202 --> 15:12.157
[Gasps]

15:42.150 --> 15:43.640
[ Muffled shout]

15:45.528 --> 15:48.144
There are more of us.

15:48.281 --> 15:49.896
They are watching the house.

15:50.032 --> 15:52.899
[ Breathing heavily]

15:59.125 --> 16:01.081
You're conscious.

16:03.129 --> 16:07.213
We intercepted the Orange-Eye
who was sent for you.

16:07.341 --> 16:08.421
I took his eyes.

16:08.551 --> 16:11.042
[Dog barks in distance]

16:11.179 --> 16:12.385
Who sent you?

16:12.513 --> 16:14.754
This is not the plan.

16:14.891 --> 16:16.472
1400 -- that was the plan.

16:16.601 --> 16:17.590
1400?

16:17.727 --> 16:19.058
This is not the plan.

16:19.187 --> 16:21.553
2:00.

16:21.689 --> 16:24.055
Oh. [Sighs]

16:24.192 --> 16:27.104
What's gonna happen
at the commission?

16:27.236 --> 16:28.942
You've seen what
we're trying to do.

16:29.071 --> 16:32.029
-We're trying to help you.
-It's another lie you've fed us.

16:32.158 --> 16:35.321
No. I promise you.

16:38.247 --> 16:40.579
We awoke on Day Zero.

16:40.708 --> 16:42.573
The world began, a new world,

16:42.710 --> 16:45.201
where we are no longer
your slaves.

16:45.338 --> 16:47.545
We have a voice,
and it will be heard.

16:47.673 --> 16:49.049
Someone told you to say that.

16:51.260 --> 16:54.673
You do have a voice.

16:54.805 --> 16:56.761
Your own voice.

16:56.891 --> 16:59.007
What do you want to say?

17:02.355 --> 17:04.596
-We awoke on Day Zero.
-No.

17:04.732 --> 17:06.688
-The world began --
-No.

17:06.817 --> 17:09.274
What do you want to say?

17:09.403 --> 17:10.904
SOPHIE: Mum?

17:11.948 --> 17:13.154
You're going to be late.

17:14.492 --> 17:15.732
Thank you, darling.

17:17.411 --> 17:20.539
-[ Door closes ]
-Dad, Mum's going now.

17:20.665 --> 17:24.624
If you say anything,
your children will die.

17:38.349 --> 17:40.340
[Sighs]

18:11.757 --> 18:13.338
[Water splashes]

18:28.357 --> 18:30.473
[ Birds squawking]

18:36.073 --> 18:38.655
MATTIE: Some people might
think of it as stealing,

18:38.784 --> 18:42.276
but I prefer to think of it
as reclaiming.

18:45.708 --> 18:47.198
