and now I'm...just...

19:53.359 --> 19:55.441
someone who used to be.

19:57.488 --> 19:59.729
You're here, Leo.

19:59.865 --> 20:01.366
You're alive.

20:02.952 --> 20:06.410
Hester tried
to kill you, but...

20:07.456 --> 20:08.992
...but she saved you.

20:09.125 --> 20:14.040
She hit the reset button,
and now you're human again.

20:14.171 --> 20:19.757
You can do anything
you want to.

20:19.885 --> 20:21.716
You can be
anything you want to.

20:23.055 --> 20:25.467
Maybe it's time
you stop looking back.

20:25.599 --> 20:27.635
Maybe it's time we both do.

20:59.175 --> 21:01.666
